### Get assets
@access_token = {{login.response.body.token}}
GET {{host}}/assets
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Get single asset
@access_token = {{login.response.body.token}}
GET {{host}}/assets/10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### Get single asset with related data
@access_token = {{login.response.body.token}}
GET {{host}}/assets/10/details
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


